casebody.data:
BALDWIN
v.
KEYCORP CORPORATE OFFICES 2018-1244 Supreme Court of Ohio. November 28, 2018

O'CONNOR, C.J., and O'DONNELL, KENNEDY, FRENCH, FISCHER, DEWINE, and DEGENARO, JJ., concur.

MERIT DECISION WITHOUT OPINION

Miscellaneous case. On S.Ct.Prac.R. 12.04 determination, cause dismissed. Relator's motion to include supporting evidence for the complaint denied. Respondent's motion for leave to file motion to dismiss denied as moot.
